XC_HIGHJUMP - longjump map
 
Hello, i want to show you my new map, by the way it's my first map,
so it isn't as great as proff climbing or jumping maps.
But the nicest stuff is not the goal of this map. The goal is to jump
as much as you can ;) But not longjump. I wondered if it's possible
to make any kind of highjump in source and it's possible.
You jump it like longjump, but i think it's more difficult.
I didn't test it much, but did 215 block :) 
 
When you jump something difficult(my opinion)
it will play sound... From 212 - 214 it's Impressive
                      From 215 - 218 it's Perfect
                      From 219 - 220 it's Wickedsick
and legendary blocks in separated room(225 and 230) plays sound GOOOOODDDDLIIIKE

THIS MAP WAS MADE TO BE PLAYED WITH DEFAULT CSS SETTINGS!!!

GL & HF improving your lj and now hj (but still lj xD) skills :)

Map by ---N00B---K!LL3R---
